room_title: Escape room "Distress Call" by Unity Escape Rooms in Pomona
room_description: You’ve been contracted by the Federation to board and repair a protype spaceship recently attacked by a Gorgonite strike team. We’ve had no contact with the crew since the attack and fear they’ve been captured. The ship is floating in the Gamma Quadrant and scanners indicate the Gorgonite strike team is still in the area. Do you have what it takes to repair and defend the ship and get it back to a federation port before the Gorgonite Armada arrives?
